  "projectName": "NKLegacy",
  "projectDescription": "A Windows NT-inspired kernel operating system for x86 (i386), written from scratch in C and x86 assembly, featuring a two-stage bootloader, protected mode, hardware drivers, a RAM filesystem, and a built-in command shell.",
