  "keyFeatures": [
    "Two-stage NKBootman bootloader (MBR → Protected Mode) and GRUB/Multiboot support",
    "Full x86 protected mode with GDT and IDT setup",
    "ISR/IRQ handling via 8259 PIC remapping",
    "8253/8254 PIT configured to 1000 Hz for system tick counting",
    "VGA text-mode driver (80×25, colors, hardware cursor, scrolling)",
    "COM1 serial debug output at 115200 baud",
    "PS/2 keyboard driver with scancode set 1 and shift support",
    "kprintf kernel formatter outputting to both VGA and serial simultaneously",
    "NKFS in-memory RAM filesystem with directory tree and file I/O",
    "Built-in NT-style command shell (DIR, CD, MKDIR, ECHO, TYPE, CLS, VER)",
    "NKBuild minimal PE binary builder and PE loader/executor",
    "Freestanding runtime string library (memset, memcpy, strlen, strcmp, etc.)"
  ],
